"2020-02-04T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"131ce4bddf380a0996a18ea4639d1c7ce51e9262","tid":1862442,"uid":335921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"490e919a7f122a605b4e5b8de39369d2b66d89f6","tid":1862442,"uid":143277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"究竟香港人奴性重啲定健康緊要啲呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:59:11.000Z","msg":"奴性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返工都仲可以搏一搏自己唔會中招<br />\n比人炒冇工開仲慘過肺炎死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反抗係叫下安慰下自己<br />\n都係口號黎姐<br />\n<br />\n我就罷咗啦，大不了搵過份<br />\n人廢咪唯有打一份工打成世囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef72d3c976bea2e2f914c1cb066b2056ad8e9de","tid":1862442,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T18:40:16.000Z","msg":"工會籌咗咁耐 要發一發市㗎啦<br />\n未入嘅一齊罷啦"},{"pid":"f1c1af9b8ef5bd608eac70f430935232b5781dc4","tid":1862442,"uid":178364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T18:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a019dfb2158bbeffad07c9182fbfa8e18abbadd","tid":1862442,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T22:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bf375e642a0174f53c8ce4c69aebffcb874da2","tid":1862442,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T23:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b7f5fa8f56274b362d2ccbc8ce001256e9ee0f","tid":1862442,"uid":188393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T23:55:55.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"61f75474317039d3d87f2c8b3029fcb1fda2a4c5","tid":1862442,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T00:00:22.000Z","msg":"突然間大量p牌同五毛狗+真心膠係度帶風嘅<br />\n表示而家爆發左就封關都無用<br />\n叫醫護復工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實情係同機場果招一樣<br />\n佢地無法破<br />\n就等大家自己放棄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一定唔可以再中港共依招<br />\n<br />\n罷到底<br />\n<br />\n唔從源頭開始減少<br />\n<br />\n做死都幾多醫護都無用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家可以明白依個道理<br />\n同埋堅定醫護個心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">各行各業而家開始配合埋港鐵工會同巴士公會<br />\n發展成全港大罷工<br />\n情願日日都係年初一<br />\n都好過武漢咁日日死城</span></span>"},{"pid":"e0552cd29c7493c940522778065b81eee52b1a1d","tid":1862442,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9923e6c5f27f1dfcf2cb131288cd8027cbf062","tid":1862442,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c527afda20177a4b27e05e6a91a1885af44a27","tid":1862442,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0a97c59f938ef02434af0b0aadbba946f474a8","tid":1862442,"uid":326665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:14:53.000Z","msg":"公共運輸，銀行金融，公務員。<br />\n只要呢三個行業，三成人罷一個月，先有機會令政府跪。<br />\n<br />\n呢個係全世界最無恥嘅政權，能贏佢唯有比佢更無恥。醫護有同理心已經輸晒。<br />\n<br />\n暫時全港得黑警做到。"},{"pid":"7404c2778061b30781dcb46e47e8545a8e32fddc","tid":1862442,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e466ca3d6abf008d674e0c9db979595ba3b0bed","tid":1862442,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"[突發]港龍工會都宣佈要搞罷工啦!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988</a>"},{"pid":"3fe7